de: Implementing Arrangement between the Swiss Federal Department of Defence, Civil Protection and Sports and the Ministry of Defence of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland concerning the Conduct of Exercise Mountain Lion 2004 - 02-11-2004 - Vereinbarung vom 2. November 2004 zwischen dem Schweizerischen Bundesrat und der Regierung des Vereinigten Königreichs von Grossbritannien und Nordirland betreffend die Durchführung militärischer Übungen oder Ausbildungen sowie die Unterstützung durch den Aufnahmestaat
en: Implementing Arrangement between the Swiss Federal Department of Defence, Civil Protection and Sports and the Ministry of Defence of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland concerning the Conduct of Exercise Mountain Lion 2004 - 02-11-2004 - Arrangement between the Swiss Federal Council and the Government of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland concerning the Conduct of Military Exercises or Training and the Provision of Host Nation Support
it: Implementing Arrangement between the Swiss Federal Department of Defence, Civil Protection and Sports and the Ministry of Defence of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland concerning the Conduct of Exercise Mountain Lion 2004 - 02-11-2004 - Accordo del 2 novembre 2004 tra il Consiglio federale svizzero e il Governo del Regno Unito di Gran Bretagna e Irlanda del Nord concernente l'esecuzione di esercitazioni o addestramenti militari e il supporto da parte dello Stato ricevente
fr: Implementing Arrangement between the Swiss Federal Department of Defence, Civil Protection and Sports and the Ministry of Defence of the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland concerning the Conduct of Exercise Mountain Lion 2004 - 02-11-2004 - Convention du 2 novembre 2004 entre le Conseil fédéral suisse et le Gouvernement du Royaume-Uni de Grande-Bretagne et d'Irlande du Nord concernant l'organisation d'exercices ou d'instruction militaires ainsi que l'appui apporté par l'Etat d'accueil
